```python
line_max=0
line_num=1
code_in=open(r"C:/Users/86158/demo.py","r").readlines()
code_out=open("demo_new.py","w")
```


```python
for i in code_in:
    if (line_max<len(i)):
        line_max=len(i)
for i in code_in:
    i=i.ljust(line_max+1).replace('\n','')+"#"+str(line_num)+"\n"
    line_num=line_num+1
    code_out.write(i)
